Class TokenScanValue

      • add

        TokenScanValue add​(TokenScanValue other)
        Adds all bits from other to this bit set. Result is a union of the two bit sets. other is kept intact.
        Parameters:
        other - value containing bits to add.
        Returns:
        this instance, now with added bits from other.

      • remove

        TokenScanValue remove​(TokenScanValue other)
        Removes all bits in other from this bit set. Result is bits in this set before the call with all bits from other removed. other is kept intact.
        Parameters:
        other - value containing bits to remove.
        Returns:
        this instance, now with removed bits from other.
